  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, TableStructureContributer<AU>, ParseFactory<AU>

    public class MultiNameFinder<AU extends AppUser,X extends MultiNameFinder>
extends AppUserNameFinder<AU,X>
    An AppUserNameFinder where multiple name mappings are held in a seperate table Configuration parameters:
    • NameFinder.realm.label label defaults to realm.
    • NameFinder.realm.table construction tag for a MultiNameFactory to hold the names
